description:
PANTS

With Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey... and special guest Mia Kirshner.


W.W.M.K.D


Kate and Leisha invite their very first special guest on to PANTS pod.

She christened the podcast, she's the third leg, she's the inimitable Mia Kirshner.




Produced and edited in the UK by Rachel Shelley.

Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod

Follow us on Instagram ThePantsPod

Record a question and email it to us: pantspodcast@yahoo.com

Music: Carol Parra @csssuxxx

Artwork: Lovefoxxx
